global variables ---can be used with in the same class and can be declared
class is an templates where objects are created
after JDK 1.7 for int,char and String , switch case statment is allowed
final keyword cannot be changed, And cannot be inherited in child class

finalize concept-- before garbage collector comes and clears the variables ,which are not being refered,or have null references, object created and no reference variable is pointing to it
gc will call finalize() method before cleaning it .Basically to do clean up activity

super keyword is used to call or inherit the property of the super class without creating an object of super class
